  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bc8\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 - \u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bb8\u0bcd, \u0b9a\u0b9c\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0b87\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0bb4\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb2 \u0b89\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b87\u0ba4\u0bcb !",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Here is the content of the written commitment between Federation - Dulles, Sajith!",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The content of the written commitment between TNA and presidential candidate Dulles and Sajith Premadasa has been released.",
        "It has been confirmed that both Dallas Alagaperuma and Sajith Premadasa, who have accepted the following conditions presented by the Federation of Tamil Nadu, have signed a written agreement in the presence of the ten members of parliament, agreeing to implement the said conditions before the end of the three to six month period and find a permanent solution and to start immediate negotiations to reach a political solution to the ethnic problem.",
        "1. To release a group of Tamil political prisoners who have been in jail for a long time without reason within a period of three months.",
        "2.Amparai District, Kalmunai North Sub-Divisional Secretariat to be upgraded to Divisional Secretariat as per Gazette Notification issued in 1991 and appointment of Accountant.",
        "3. Immediately stop the surveying work carried out by the land surveying department in order to permanently provide the troops who are camping in the private lands of the Tamil people in the north and east and in the government lands of public use.",
        "4. Stop the encroachment of Northern and Eastern Tamil lands by the Department of Archaeology, Mahavali Development Authority, Department of Forestry, Department of Wildlife, Department of Mineral Resources etc.",
        "5. Immediate repeal of the Anti-Terrorism Act and early disclosure of goodwill signals.",
        "7. Take immediate action to establish justice and find out the truth for the missing persons.",
        "8. To evict the soldiers from the private lands in the North and East and to enable our people who are still refugees in their own country to settle in their native lands.",
        "9. Military presence in North and East; Reducing and making way for the normal life of the people.",
        "10. Initiate immediate negotiations without delay for a political settlement of the rights of the Tamils \u200b\u200bwho have been displaced in this country for more than eighty years."
      ],
